1
00:00:03,021 --> 00:00:08,021
CADENCE. Adaptive PME tutor for every Marine.

2
00:00:08,024 --> 00:00:13,024
PME training problem: one-size-fits-all is not working at the artifact level.

3
00:00:13,029 --> 00:00:18,029
Three demo courses. Three Marines. One personalized study plan each.

4
00:00:18,031 --> 00:00:24,031
Marine logs in. CADENCE reads their docx submission and last 10 forum posts.

5
00:00:24,042 --> 00:00:30,042
Three-stage agent. Read. Analyze. Plan.

6
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:38,100
A Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts the one-page Adaptive Study Plan.

7
00:00:32,108 --> 00:00:39,108
Knowledge gaps. Doctrine to review. Three tailored study questions.

8
00:00:39,118 --> 00:00:45,118
Seven-day learning targets. Daily action. Rubric-aligned writing tips.

9
00:00:45,127 --> 00:00:52,127
Privacy Act of 1974 and DoDI 1322.35. NAVMC 3500 T&R cited. SHA-256 chained. Data stays in the SCIF.

10
00:00:52,136 --> 00:01:00,136
Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. From Context to Action. Deploy in hours.
